00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:40.350
Because we know no one's going
to reach into that pocket.

00:07:40.350 --> 00:07:43.750
No claims on it, but
I get to promote it.

00:07:43.750 --> 00:07:46.350
So, this pocket actually
on the newer garments

00:07:46.350 --> 00:07:48.630
