Well, we just moved
it down a little lower

00:10:03.640 --> 00:10:04.660
so that it's down here.

00:10:04.660 --> 00:10:09.680
So that's the basis for
SCOTTeVEST and the clothing.

00:10:09.680 --> 00:10:13.970
Now, my story is
really about my passion

00:10:13.970 --> 00:10:17.040
and just going around and being
in opportunities like this.

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:19.750
I never turn down an opportunity
to talk about my product,

00:10:19.750 --> 00:10:20.750
