And using the
internet, it's enabled

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:26.607
me to view the
world differently,

00:10:26.607 --> 00:10:28.190
and I've done this
from the beginning.

00:10:28.190 --> 00:10:32.010
I send video messages because
passion doesn't come through

00:10:32.010 --> 00:10:32.860
