Scott, why are you so angry?

00:10:47.270 --> 00:10:47.853
I'm not angry.

00:10:47.853 --> 00:10:50.170
I'm just really
excited about it.

00:10:50.170 --> 00:10:53.750
So what I've done
for a very long time

00:10:53.750 --> 00:10:58.800
